==Ancient Greek==

===Pronunciation===
*ὀφθαλμός / ophthalmos / of-thal-mos'

===eymology===
*From G3700; the eye (literally or figuratively); by implication vision; figuratively envy (from the jealous side glance): 

===Noun===
'''ὀφθαλμός'''

# [[eye]], [[sight]].

